<l>vīḻvāri ṉiṉcoṟ peṟāa tulakattu </l>
<l> vāḻvāriṉ vaṉkaṇā ril</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>There is no one in the world so hard-hearted as those who can live without receiving (even) a kind word from their beloved.</l>
